<h1 align="center">Solis AI</h1>

<p align="center">
Video repurposing system that transforms long-form content into structured, reusable video outputs using template-based generation.
</p>

<p align="center">
Upload a YouTube video. Solis AI extracts structure, segments content, and generates new formats through customizable templates.
</p>

---

## System Overview

Solis AI is built to convert unstructured video content into structured media assets.

It focuses on deterministic transformation rather than manual editing.

---

## Pipeline

Input → Ingestion → Content Analysis → Segmentation → Template Mapping → Render Output

---

## Capabilities

- Video structure extraction from YouTube sources  
- Segment-based content reconstruction  
- Template-driven rendering system  
- Multi-format output generation  
- Fully customizable visual system  

---

## Design System

The visual layer is driven by a token-based system:

- Primary: `#f97316`
- Deep: `#c2410c`
- Surface: translucent layered UI
- Ink: deep neutral contrast system
- Gradients: warm orange spectrum

---

## Output Philosophy

Solis AI prioritizes:
- structured transformation over manual editing  
- reusable content systems over one-off outputs  
- scalable templates over static video creation  

---
